title: "On-Care: AI-powered chronic disease management platform for 20-30s hypertension and diabetes risk groups"
abstract: >-
  On-Care is a Flutter-based cross-platform healthcare application targeting
  the 20-30 age group at risk of hypertension and diabetes. It integrates
  Vision AI food recognition (YOLOv8 + Gemini Vision + Korean public nutrition
  database), RAG-based personalized health coaching (LangChain + Pinecone +
  GPT-4o), and offline-to-online trainer connectivity, addressing the three
  structural limitations of existing healthcare apps — recording friction,
  context-less generic advice, and online-offline disconnection.
